{"tid":1759313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"別忘了彥霖之死","createTime":"2019-11-27T14:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T08:43:42.000Z","uid":241108,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd00c391bb4609434304e4f7674ca98f355c07e","tid":1759313,"uid":241108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n【尋找陳彥霖媽媽】<br />\n<br />\n有住喺天水圍嘅街坊話呢半個月已經唔見陳媽媽有出入過住所，而與彥霖同住嘅公公，亦有元朗街坊話成個幾月冇見過佢公公。有記者曾經多次拍門亦冇人應。<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB聲稱佢地獨家訪問果位係陳彥霖媽媽，而警方又話跳樓果位唔係陳彥霖媽媽。咁到底陳彥霖媽媽去左邊?<br />\n<br />\n懇請大家傳開去，唔可以令呢件事被淡化<br />\n(我知香港人好善忘)，<br />\n全香港有388位民主派區議員當選，針對連月嚟嘅非尋常自殺個案，佢地係咪應該成立小組去徹底調查/或者請專家調查?"},{"pid":"af10051b6dc3fa59774c9c8b4061d9558d26a44c","tid":1759313,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"pish ar 屌"},{"pid":"d1ff4a96e0cb275b165e4e360f64cbf164ee6e00","tid":1759313,"uid":316538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T14:39:06.000Z","msg":"仲有周同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05337c147f561a1393670075af8e1437d5f05cb","tid":1759313,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:39:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>推呀！<br />\n<br />\n兩母女咁就死咗！<br />\n<br />\n仲有天理嘅！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf49c5b5fc6b083b7db15069ef1a47a45a2757bd","tid":1759313,"uid":114673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T00:55:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b73a5ecc3de38711c3f0190f45d1a929eccecc01","tid":